relation: Variation 1) Shadow Grapevines: 1-3 Open Left, Man Chassé Back-Lady 3 Steps to Shadow, 2 Grapevines, Forward into Hover, Man Chassé Back to Right ? Lady 3 Steps Right, Developé, 4-6 Open Left Ending.

Variation 2) Shadow Sway Step: Twinkle & Chair, Explosions, Man Rock Right Foot & Left Foot, Lady 3 Steps to Shadow, Sway Step, Man Chassé, Lady 3 Steps Right, Man Roll Lady Back In, 4-6 Open Left Ending.
Variation 3) Advanced Back Hand to Hand: Twinkle to Promenade, Check Across on Inside Foot to Syncopated 3 Step Turn, Crossbody Lead, Backward Hand to Hand, 4-6 Left Box Ending.
Variaition 4) Outside Swivel & Chassé to Step Points: Twinkle to Open Right, Outside Swivel with Tumble Turn Ending, Back into Chassé, 2 Step Point, Hairpin, Open Impetus, 4-6 Open Left Ending.
Review - Variations 1-4 in a routine format.

Variation 5) Runaround to Side by Side Grapevines: 1-3 Open Left, Hairpin, Runaround, Man Open Impetus, Lady Spin Off, Grapevine, Man Check on Right Foot, Lady Turn Right Back to Man, Developé, Open Left Ending.
Variation 6) Double Reverse Overspin with Advance Gem Ending: Double Reverse Overspin, Back Wing (Gem), Step Point x 2 into Developé, Back Chassé into Grapevine, Rondé into Weave Ending.
Variation 7) Side by Side Weave: Promenade Twinkles, Side by Side Weave, Chassé Turn to Line Of Dance, Crossbody Lead, Flip Flop Lady to Right, Progressive Ending.

Variation 8) Shadow Step Points: Twinkle, Crossbody, Open Fallaway, Man 2 Steps Forward, Lady Curl into Shadow, Progressive in Shadow, 2 Step Point in Shadow, Man Chassé Turning Right, Lady 3 Steps to Outside Partner, 4-6 Back Open Left Ending.
Review - Variations 5-8 in a routine format.
